info.name: pygmtools
info.summary: pygmtools provides graph matching solvers in Python and supports various computational backends: numpy and pytorch. pygmtools also provides API for preprocessing dataset, fetching data and evaluating prediction result for graph matching on several datasets, including PascalVOC, WillowObject, CUB2011, IMC-PT-SparseGM and SPair71k.
